Adjust DVDAuthor.xml, Menu.xml and other files and use
one of the commands:

1. Write DVD Folder           - "scons"
2. Clean                      - "scons -c"
3. Play Authored DVD in Totem - "scons totem"
3.1. --||-- in Xine           - "scons xine"
4. Write Disk Image (.iso)    - "scons dvd.iso"
5. Burn to DVD                - "scons burn"

